title: Dating Harry would include... Part 2
body:
View part one here


  • probably being friends before you start to date
  • when you start to date he’d still take you on a real first date though
  • telling your friends after a few weeks in
  • trying to keep your relationship out of the media for as long as possible
  • still, him posting really cute couple pics on his private insta (i’m really sure he has one tbh)
  • having a cute pic as lockscreen, maybe even matching
  • eventually, when you’ ve been spotted by paps numerous times and been together for quite some time, you’d decide you don’t want to hide your love anymore
  • he’d still be really private about it though
  • but you’d be his plus one to many events
  • holding hands ALL the time
  • that’s mostly all of the PDA there is
  • maybe he’d give you a kiss on the cheek or temple or maybe he’d place his hand on the small of your back
  • but that’s about it
  • still, everybody could see how much in love the two of you were
  • loving glances
  • making sure you’d be comfortable and safe
  • squeezing your hand reassuringly
  • you’d probably wear something slightly matching to events
  • like he’d wear one of his suits and you’d be wearing at least a little accessoire in the same colour
  • literally the best dressed couple
  • when he’d be asked about you, his whole face would light up

summary: locals don't understand that when young girls say harry is literally their reason to live, damn they actually mean every single...
body:
locals don’t understand that when young girls say harry is literally their reason to live, damn they actually mean every single word of it cos harry is like the sunshine lightening up my world and helping me conquer all my fears and sadness.

locals don’t understand when girls say they are in love harry and willing to do everything for him, this doesn’t mean I wanna marry him, I just wanna be his best friend and be happy and supportive for him whenever he finds love and happiness in his life.
